WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.791 --> 00:00:03.250
Thank you for your
contribution

2
00:00:08.458 --> 00:00:10.666
We are the future
world rulers

3
00:00:10.666 --> 00:00:12.166
I knew it!

4
00:00:12.166 --> 00:00:14.125
13 people will stay behind me

5
00:00:14.125 --> 00:00:18.500
And 5 - you have no choice
but to follow the others

6
00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:19.750
Men, all stand up!

7
00:00:20.333 --> 00:00:23.333
Now the main goal is
only warfare

8
00:00:23.333 --> 00:00:24.500
Everything else takes a back seat

9
00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:27.500
Men, gather by the door!
We're going to build a barricade

10
00:00:27.500 --> 00:00:30.000
Women, come to the heart
of the community, quickly!

11
00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:33.000
You will take care of children,
patch up the wounded

12
00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:36.250
Now you really only obey
your role

13
00:00:36.250 --> 00:00:39.041
Forget everything that's
outside your role

14
00:00:39.041 --> 00:00:41.291
I will use everything
that's been brought

15
00:00:41.291 --> 00:00:43.000
Pocket knives, switchblades,
revolvers

16
00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:46.541
We'll fill condoms with whiskey,
light them up, and throw them

17
00:00:46.541 --> 00:00:48.875
We'll tie them up
with McGyver's tape

18
00:00:48.875 --> 00:00:51.500
We'll tape their mouths shut.
They won't be able to say anything!

19
00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:55.791
I have a piano -
You can play them unconscious with the piano!

20
00:01:00.458 --> 00:01:01.791
Very good!

21
00:01:13.041 --> 00:01:14.541
Everything went so well, right?!

22
00:01:18.208 --> 00:01:21.750
We'll meet later

23
00:01:23.416 --> 00:01:26.333
Discuss how to proceed
together...